and I can't even help my best friend.

554
00:34:17,580 --> 00:34:18,460
So, Qinlan,

555
00:34:19,760 --> 00:34:20,620
is there really

556
00:34:22,400 --> 00:34:24,280
a utopia in this world?

557
00:34:29,710 --> 00:34:31,630
Miss Huaizhu, we have a visitor.

558
00:34:31,800 --> 00:34:33,510
He claimed to be the Master of the Nangong family

559
00:34:33,510 --> 00:34:36,000
and specifically asked to see you, Miss Huaizhu.

560
00:34:36,000 --> 00:34:37,030
Nangong Ye?

561
00:34:38,150 --> 00:34:39,480
The Inspection Bureau?

562
00:34:51,360 --> 00:34:52,360
Mr. Nangong.

563
00:34:55,880 --> 00:34:57,230
Sir, what brings you

564
00:34:57,230 --> 00:34:58,760
here today?

565
00:34:58,760 --> 00:35:00,220
Please feel free to speak.

566
00:35:00,590 --> 00:35:03,190
Miss Dongfang, you're quite straightforward.

567
00:35:03,190 --> 00:35:06,250
There's indeed something I'd like to discuss with you.

568
00:35:06,800 --> 00:35:09,000
The Yiqi Alliance is deeply corrupted.

569
00:35:09,000 --> 00:35:10,670
The blame lies with the Wangquan family.

570
00:35:10,670 --> 00:35:12,510
I am determined to replace them.

571
00:35:13,230 --> 00:35:16,030
I humbly request your assistance, Miss Dongfang,

572
00:35:16,030 --> 00:35:18,430
in capturing and killing Wangquan Hongye.

573
00:35:19,760 --> 00:35:20,760
Mr. Nangong,

574
00:35:21,880 --> 00:35:22,760
what can I get

575
00:35:23,400 --> 00:35:24,360
if I help you?

576
00:35:27,710 --> 00:35:30,040
As long as we can bring down the Wangquans,

577
00:35:30,280 --> 00:35:31,440
I can give you

578
00:35:32,070 --> 00:35:33,440
whatever you need.

579
00:35:38,710 --> 00:35:42,190
Young Master, you just rejected Nangong Ye's proposal to attack Nanchui,

580
00:35:42,190 --> 00:35:44,590
so he's now holding a grand sword-opening ceremony.

581
00:35:44,590 --> 00:35:45,940
At this ceremony,

582
00:35:46,230 --> 00:35:49,760
he will surely propose to promote using demon cores in sword forging.

583
00:35:49,760 --> 00:35:51,280
If you reject it again,

584
00:35:51,360 --> 00:35:54,090
it will be openly making an enemy of the Nangongs.

585
00:35:54,840 --> 00:35:56,170
We are already enemies.

586
00:35:56,800 --> 00:35:59,260
It's just making the hostility aboveboard.

587
00:36:00,030 --> 00:36:02,030
Will you go attend it, Young Master?

588
00:36:02,670 --> 00:36:04,440
For the treacherous banquet in ten days,

589
00:36:04,440 --> 00:36:06,440
inform Zui to bring Yang Yitan along

590
00:36:06,630 --> 00:36:07,510
and go attend it with me.
